{"tid":2233545,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六旬退休漢大叫「將三萬香港法西斯警察全部殺晒」 被控公眾地方擾亂秩序受審","createTime":"2020-10-07T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T09:44:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4ffbd06c6b500c6cd798510413739c4e2d8fdb","tid":2233545,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"民間集會團隊今年1月在中環遮打花園舉行「天下制裁」集會，其間一名六旬退休漢被指在金鐘港鐵站外以大聲公宣稱要「將三萬香港法西斯警察全部殺晒」，數天後被捕。涉案退休漢否認公眾地方擾亂秩序行為罪，今在東區裁判法院受審。目擊事發經過的警員接受辯方盤問時承認，當時現場無人堵路，亦無人衝擊警方、刑事毀壞或傷人，警員亦沒有使用防暴裝備。<br />\n<br />\n機動部隊F大連第三小隊警署警長李泰萊供稱，今年1月19日和同袍到金鐘樂禮街設立防線，未幾前往金鐘港鐵站B出口外支援。當時港鐵站出口有約300名示威者聚集，情緒激動，並大聲講粗口及叫囂。警方向示威者展示藍旗警告，及後大部份示威者離去，警員亦後退。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/7TNHWZRMJVAPXK4MQ4LBKCLHYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F7TNHWZRMJVAPXK4MQ4LBKCLHYY%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=9057e0ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F7TNHWZRMJVAPXK4MQ4LBKCLHYY%2F&h=cffaa2e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/7TNHWZRMJVAPXK4MQ4LBKCLHYY/</a>"},{"pid":"e6fb5e6205051d7cbeca925731aff538666154a8","tid":2233545,"uid":54623,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"阿叔識野. 識指出班警察係法西斯<br />\n香港法西斯政權"},{"pid":"406f385ec1c5b5c5f0cbf5bfd6255178e9f87cd5","tid":2233545,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"而家香港真係法西斯政權"},{"pid":"3fe21d80679f3f5cc11f60e2addf557d37b70551","tid":2233545,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g